aurora-jobhopper (0.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  Relevant changes since 0.1:
  * Fix shutdown handling: ^C now actually exits
  * Default to localhost for zookeeper
  * Set probably-useless defaults for --scheduler_url and --base_domain
  * Don't special-case single instance jobs
  * Extend multi-cluster support
  * Change zk_basepath default to match aurora's default
  * Refactor to remove use of private aurora apis
  * Rename entrypoint to __main__.py

 -- Benjamin Staffin <benley@gmail.com>  Tue, 26 Jan 2016 00:12:27 +0000
